data.description: Nestled in the heart of a classic neighborhood, this 1951 colonial home exudes timeless charm and character.  Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this residence offers a total living space of approximately 2,009 square feet.  Newer roof,  new high efficiency boiler, new water heater, upgraded plumbing and electrical.  Beautifully renovated family room addition featuring vinyl plank flooring , mini split, floor to ceiling stone fireplace with pellet stove insert.   Brand new floor in the kitchen and hardwoods through out 2nd floor.  1 st floor laundry off the kitchen for added convenience! The backyard features a  brick courtyard/patio off of the enclosed pool area with a sauna and spa!  Perfect for indoor and outdoor entertaining.  Its classic design, combined with the potential for personalization and updates, makes it a wonderful canvas for your dream home. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of history with this charming colonial residence.  SELLER IS OFFERING A $3000 DECORATING ALLOWANCE WITH AN ACCEPTABLE OFFER!!
